NAME
        looks - alter your looks

SYNOPSIS
	looks
	looks <attribute>
	looks <attribute> <value>
	looks confirm

DESCRIPTION
	Until a certain age, young players have the possibility to amend their
	looks if they aren't completely satisfied with their first choices.
	This can only be done in a location where you can also meditate.

OPTIONS
	[none]   - display your current looks.
	<attrib> - display the possible list of values for an attribute.
	<value>  - set a value to an attribute.
	confirm  - when done, confirm changes to make them stick.

SEE ALSO
	meditate
